The Sphere of the Earth
=======================

Educational and museographic project for science museums and exhibitions, about cartography, maps and the geometry of the sphere.

Author:		Daniel Ramos
Email:		daniel.ramos@imaginary.org
Repository:	https://github.com/danielramosg/sphereofearth
Copyright (C) 2013 - 2015  Daniel Ramos


